Well, because you two have already posted videos of a personal nature to the internet and the probability of you both proposing at the same time with the same ring box is highly unlikely, I do believe that you are not being truthful. Sure someone else posted the video, but judging from all the photos that were taken and all the videos of this even that are posted to youtube, I still believe this was staged by you and your partner for internet fame. You both knew that your friends would post the videos. 

I call bullshit and find it sad that today's society has still not really accepted same sex relationships as being "normal". That is the only reason why this video is popular. It is because people find it "cute" that two women would get engaged to each other. If you two were ugly or men...this would not reach 1000 views. I do believe that you both love the attention. I didn't expect for you to actually tell the truth and admit it was staged, because you need to save face and all the people who up voted you would turn against you in a second. 

I also find that you exploiting your sexuality to get up votes is appalling. I find it normal for two men, two women, one man one woman, to have sex and get married and not in that order. I guess that we have not reached the time that society thinks that its normal. 

People believe what they want to believe and if they pretend that they think that the double engagement was a surprise to you both, then let them live in their fantasy but it is so painfully obvious that you two planned it.
